Okay, as for where you can
find the ingredients...

rows.label: qst720402_msg0002
rows.name:
Grimdark Crabs can be
gathered at the water's
edge in many parts of Iira...

rows.label: qst720402_msg0003
rows.name:
You'll have to hunt the Sowl Feris
that live nearby to get their
meat, so we can preserve it.

rows.label: qst720402_msg0004
rows.name:
You can pick Lactonuts
on the grasslands.

rows.label: qst720402_msg0005
rows.name: And same for the Weeping Flour.

rows.label: qst720402_msg0006
rows.name: Alright everyone, I'm counting on you.
